<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= typeof title !== 'undefined' ? title : 'БД Мебельной компании' %></title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #2c3e50;
            --secondary-color: #34495e;
            --accent-color: #3498db;
            --success-color: #27ae60;
            --danger-color: #e74c3c;
            --warning-color: #f39c12;
            --light-bg: #ecf0f1;
            --border-color: #bdc3c7;
            --text-primary: #2c3e50;
            --text-secondary: #7f8c8d;
            --shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f5f7fa;
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            min-height: 100vh;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        
        header {
            background: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            padding: 24px 40px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--accent-color);
        }
        
        header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        
        header p {
            font-size: 13px;
            opacity: 0.8;
            margin-top: 4px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        
        nav {
            background: white;
            padding: 0 40px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        nav a {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        
        nav a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            border-bottom-color: var(--accent-color);
            background: rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.05);
        }
        
        nav a.active {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            border-bottom-color: var(--accent-color);
        }
        
        main {
            padding: 32px 40px;
            max-width: 100%;
        }
        
        h2 {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            padding-bottom: 12px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--light-bg);
        }
        
        h3 {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .btn {
            background: var(--accent-color);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            background: #2980b9;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }
        
        .btn-danger {
            background: var(--danger-color);
        }
        
        .btn-danger:hover {
            background: #c0392b;
        }
        
        .btn-success {
            background: var(--success-color);
        }
        
        .btn-success:hover {
            background: #229954;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background: var(--secondary-color);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #2c3e50;
        }
        
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: separate;
            border-spacing: 0;
            margin-top: 20px;
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 4px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        th, td {
            padding: 14px 16px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        
        th {
            background: var(--light-bg);
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-size: 13px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        td {
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        tr:hover {
            background: rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.03);
        }
        
        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }
        
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }
        
        .stat-card {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            padding: 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-color);
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        
        .stat-card:hover {
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .stat-card h3 {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--accent-color);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .stat-card p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .search-box {
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
            width: 320px;
            margin-right: 8px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        
        .search-box:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--accent-color);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.1);
        }
        
        form {
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        input, select, textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            font-family: inherit;
        }
        
        input:focus, select:focus, textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--accent-color);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.1);
        }
        
        .alert {
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-left: 4px solid;
        }
        
        .alert-success {
            background: #d5f4e6;
            color: #0f5132;
            border-left-color: var(--success-color);
        }
        
        .alert-danger {
            background: #f8d7da;
            color: #842029;
            border-left-color: var(--danger-color);
        }
        
        .toolbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            padding: 16px;
            background: var(--light-bg);
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .badge-success {
            background: #d5f4e6;
            color: var(--success-color);
        }
        
        .badge-danger {
            background: #f8d7da;
            color: var(--danger-color);
        }
        
        .info-text {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-top: 16px;
        }
        
        strong {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>База данных мебельной компании</h1>
            <p>Система управления продукцией</p>
        </header>
        
        <nav>
            <a href="/">Главная</a>
            <a href="/products">Продукция</a>
            <a href="/workshops">Цеха</a>
            <a href="/analytics">Аналитика</a>
        </nav>
        
        <main>
            <%- body %>
        </main>
    </div>
    
    <footer style="background: #2c3e50; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 20px; margin-top: 40px;">
        <p>&copy; 2006–2025 Furniture Company. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
